&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Fusion/Saber Saw Operator – Construction Resources Surfaces (Decatur, GA)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Overview&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;Construction Resources Surfaces is looking for a reliable, detail‑focused individual to join our fabrication team as a &lt;strong&gt;Fusion/Saber Saw Operator&lt;/strong&gt;. This position involves working with automated cutting equipment to support the processing of stone and surface materials for residential and commercial projects.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Operate and monitor a Fusion/Saber automated saw system&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Review job specifications and follow production requirements to ensure accurate cuts&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist with staging materials before cutting and organizing completed pieces afterward&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Perform routine equipment checks and report any issues to the supervisor&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain a clean, safe, and organized work environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide general support to shop operations as needed&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Qualifications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Preferably &lt;strong&gt;2–3 years of experience&lt;/strong&gt; in fabrication, manufacturing, or machine operation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Previous Electric Saw experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to learn and operate automated or computer‑assisted machinery&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Comfortable working in a fast‑paced production environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong attention to detail and ability to follow established procedures&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Dependable, team‑oriented, and committed to consistent attendance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Work Environment&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;This role is based in our Decatur, Georgia facility and involves hands‑on work with stone materials and industrial cutting equipment.&lt;/p&gt;
