&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Warehouse and Day Operations responsibilities:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The Warehouse Picker/Receiver is expected to lead by example and ensure all projects and day to day work is performed in accordance with company standards.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;This position is expected to work closely with the Tile Warehouse Manager on a daily basis.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A warehouse Picker/ Receiver is both a receiver and a picker tasked with loading and unloading of inbound/outbound trucks in a timely manner.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Organizing and putting away material in designated locations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Communicate all discovered or suspected material damage or inventory issues to the Tile Warehouse Manager.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Pulling/compiling customer orders onto consolidated pallets.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Wrapping up and banding pallets after being put together to ensure safe delivery.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Loading and Unloading trucks.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Aid in customer pickups where material is expected to be safely put into residential vehicles.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work together with coworkers to pull large and awkward boxes and pieces.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;This position will assist in the container receipt process including physically unloading materials &amp;amp; making system inputs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work with the operations team on all projects that aid in the improvement and advancement of our overall operations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain a safe and clean work area.&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Job Requirements:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Availability to work Monday – Friday during the window of 7:30 am - 5:00 pm.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The ability to lift and move heavy boxes 50-75 lbs. Regularly.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Knowledge and experience with forklifts and reach machines required. At least 1-year prior experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Must have reliable transportation to get to and from work.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Must be able to stand for long periods of time.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
