&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Overview&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Inside Sales role ensures that all customer needs are promptly addressed in a courteous and professional manner. Will assist staff with all aspects of the sales and execution process. Acts as a liaison between customer and Outside Sales team operations team to provide a high level of customer service. The Inside Sales role is critical to ensuring a smooth and efficient sales process, contributing to customer satisfaction and overall business success.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Essential Functions:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage customer orders by assisting Outside Sales team with quotations, order placement, product fulfillment, scheduling, and support after the sale&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage order entry in ERP&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with operations team to secure needed product&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage customer portals and communicate scheduling changes with appropriate team members&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Communicate any credit issues discovered upon order entry to appropriate sales personnel&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Answer incoming calls or emails; timely &amp;amp; professionally&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Perform other duties as required&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Competencies/Skills/Abilities:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;High School Diploma or GED required&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong organizational skills and effective team player&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to be detail-oriented and multi-task, work within specified timeframes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong verbal and written communication skills are required, Bi-lingual English/Spanish is a plus&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Previous Customer Service work experience is required; previous work experience in our industry is preferred&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficient with Microsoft Office; Outlook, Excel and Word&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Personal Attributes:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Positive Attitude – Cooperation, Courteous, Friendly, Honest, Respectful&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Teamwork – Collaborative, Team Player, Accept Feedback, Customer Service, Emotional Intelligence, Interpersonal Skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work Ethic – Multi-tasking, Organization, Time management &amp;amp; Efficiency, Strategic Planning, Results Oriented&lt;/li&gt;
